---
title: Blueberry-BBQ Chicken Thighs with Roasted Potatoes and Spinach Salad
description: Sometimes the best things in life are unexpected—like this delicious combination of blueberry jam and BBQ sauce. This pairing adds a little something special to this classic chicken dinner, which is rounded out with roasted potatoes and a bright spring mix salad.
